description: Adds a member (user or group) to the group's set.

parameters.name: OrganizationId
parameters.description: The organization under which the group exists.

parameters.name: GroupId
parameters.description: The group to which the member (user or group) is associated. The identifier can accept GroupId, Groupname, or email. The following identity formats are available: Group ID: 12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012 or S-1-1-12-1234567890-123456789-123456789-1234 Email address: group@domain.tld Group name: group.

parameters.name: MemberId
parameters.description: The member (user or group) to associate to the group. The member ID can accept UserID or GroupId, Username or Groupname, or email. Member: 12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012 or S-1-1-12-1234567890-123456789-123456789-1234 Email address: member@domain.tld Member name: member.
